title: 'Best car wash ever' features LED light show | Weird News
text:
ATLANTA (UPI) -- An Atlanta motorist traveled through a car wash with flashing LED lights and his passenger captured the experience with the "best car wash ever" on camera.
The video, posted to YouTube by 3MTCreations, features two men traveling through a Fast Trac car wash in Atlanta and capturing the experience on camera.
The car wash flashes LED lights while the vehicle's exterior is cleaned and A$AP Rocky's "LSD" plays on the radio.
A projected message scrolling across the vehicle's windshield reads, "Thank you for choosing Fast Trac."
